  "A political subdivision of a country when viewed through a simplified analytical lens": "",
  "A region is an area on Earth's surface that shares one or more common characteristics (physical, cultural, economic, or perceptual) that differentiate it from surrounding areas. It is a fundamental organizational concept in geography.": "",
  "The area around Atlanta, Georgia where people commute to downtown jobs, shop at Atlanta malls, and receive Atlanta television broadcasts defines what type of region? What would happen to this region if a major employer relocated from downtown Atlanta to a suburb?": "",
